token_info.name: BRAZIL'S MAP, SPECIAL COVID-19
token_info.description: A social and political criticism of the disgovernment that the Brazilian population lives in the pandemic period of COVID-19 (345,000 DEATHS. 4,190 DEATHS in 24h). Hunger, deaths and unemployment mark the genocidal Brazil of Jair Bolsonaro. Uma crítica social e politica ao desgoverno que a população brasileira vive no período pandêmico de COVID-19 (345 MIL MORTES. 4.190 MORTES EM 24h).
